abstract: Benoit Paire defeats David Goffin to advance to Swedish Open tennis tournament quarterfinals.
lead_paragraph: Benoit Paire ousted top-seeded David Goffin, 6-2, 6-3, at the Swedish Open in Bastad, Sweden, to reach his first quarterfinals in 15 months.

headline.main: Top-Seeded David Goffin Out in Sweden
